---

## ✨ Features

- **Live wildfire locations** from NB ERD Public Fires layer.
- **Status-based fire icons** (Out of Control, Contained, Under Control, Being Patrolled).
- **Active wildfire perimeters** with area labels (zoom-dependent visibility).
- **Weather station markers** with wind direction, speed, temperature, and humidity.
- **AQHI (Air Quality Health Index)** stations with color-coded risk categories.
- **VIIRS satellite hotspots** from NASA FIRMS.
- **Smoke plume imagery**.
- **Crown lands boundaries** (visible only when zoomed in).
- **Burn ban status** from NB burn categories service.
- **Aircraft tracking** via OpenSky Network (with whitelist highlighting).
- **Fire risk map** from CWFIS (Canadian Wildland Fire Information System).
- **Sentinel-2C imagery** overlay.
- **City labels** for major NB communities.
- **Responsive design** with simplified mobile UI.

---

## 🔧 Technology Stack

- [Leaflet](https://leafletjs.com/) — base mapping library
- [Esri Leaflet](https://esri.github.io/esri-leaflet/) & [Esri Leaflet Image](https://esri.github.io/esri-leaflet/api-reference/esri-leaflet-image.html) — ArcGIS service integration
- [Font Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/) — icons
- [OpenSky Network API](https://opensky-network.org/) — aircraft positions
- CSS custom properties for theme colors & layout

---

## 📡 Data Sources

| Layer / Feature                | Source & Link |
|--------------------------------|---------------|
| **NB Active Wild Fires**       | [GNB ArcGIS Public Fires](https://gis-erd-der.gnb.ca/arcgis/rest/services/Fire_Dashboards/Public_Fires/MapServer/0) |
| **Weather Stations**           | [Environment Canada NB Stations](https://services.arcgis.com/zmLUiqh7X11gGV2d/ArcGIS/rest/services/EnvironmentCanada/FeatureServer/0) |
| **AQHI**                       | [AQHI Stations Observations Realtime](https://services.arcgis.com/wjcPoefzjpzCgffS/ArcGIS/rest/services/aqhi_stations_observations_realtime/FeatureServer/1) |
| **Fire Perimeters**            | [Active Wildfire Perimeters in Canada (View)](https://services.arcgis.com/wjcPoefzjpzCgffS/ArcGIS/rest/services/Active_Wildfire_Perimeters_in_Canada_View/FeatureServer/0) |
| **Crown Lands**                 | [GNB Open Data Crown Lands](https://gis-erd-der.gnb.ca/server/rest/services/OpenData/Crown_Lands/FeatureServer/0) |
| **Burn Bans**                   | [GNB Burn Categories](https://gis-erd-der.gnb.ca/gisserver/rest/services/FireWeather/BurnCategories/MapServer) |
| **VIIRS Hotspots**              | [NASA FIRMS VIIRS Fire Activity](https://firms.modaps.eosdis.nasa.gov/) via ArcGIS |
| **Smoke Imagery**               | [ESRI Hosted ImageServer](https://enterpriseim.esriservices.ca/server/rest/services/Hosted/Aug12/ImageServer) |
| **Fire Risk Map**               | [CWFIS Geoserver WMS](https://cwfis.cfs.nrcan.gc.ca/geoserver/public/wms) |
| **Sentinel-2C Imagery**         | [Sentinel-2 ArcGIS ImageServer](https://sentinel.arcgis.com/arcgis/rest/services/Sentinel2/ImageServer) |
| **Aircraft**                    | [OpenSky Network API](https://opensky-network.org/api/states/all) |
| **NB Boundary**                 | [Provinces and Territories of Canada Layer](https://services.arcgis.com/wjcPoefzjpzCgffS/ArcGIS/rest/services/Provinces_and_Territories_of_Canada/FeatureServer/0) |
| **City Locations**              | Static in-code coordinates |

